{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Firefox 56 for developers","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/56","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Firefox developer release notes</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases\">Firefox developer release notes</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Add-ons</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/Add-ons/WebExtensions\">Browser extensions</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/Add-ons/Themes\">Themes</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Firefox internals</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/\">Mozilla project</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Gecko\">Gecko</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Headless_mode\">Headless mode</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/JavaScript_code_modules\">JavaScript code modules</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/js-ctypes\">JS-ctypes</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/MathML_Project\">MathML project</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/MFBT\">MFBT</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Projects\">Mozilla projects</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Preferences\">Preference system</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/WebIDL_bindings\">WebIDL bindings</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XPCOM\">XPCOM</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL\">XUL</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Building and contributing</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions\">Build instructions</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions/Configuring_Build_Options\">Configuring build options</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions/How_Mozilla_s_build_system_works\">How the build system works</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Source_Code/Mercurial\">Mozilla source code</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Localization\">Localization</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Mercurial\">Mercurial</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/QA\">Quality assurance</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Using_Mozilla_code_in_other_projects\">Using Mozilla code in other projects</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"änderungen_für_web-entwickler","title":"Änderungen für Web-Entwickler","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div><article class=\"text-content\" id=\"wikiArticle\">\n<p>Dieser Artikel enthält Informationen über die Änderungen in Firefox 56, die Entwickler betreffen. Firefox 56 ist die aktuelle <a href=\"https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/channel/desktop/#beta\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Beta-Version von Firefox</a> und wird am <a href=\"https://wiki.mozilla.org/RapidRelease/Calendar#Future_branch_dates\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">26. September 2017</a> veröffentlicht werden</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"entwicklerwerkzeuge\">Entwicklerwerkzeuge</h3>\n\n<p><em>Keine Änderungen.</em></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"html\">HTML</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Implementiert die Label-Eigenschaft für beschreibbare Formular-Steuerelemente, zum Beispiel <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/labels\"><code>HTMLInputElement.labels</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=556743\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;556743</a>).</li>\n <li>Implementiert <code>&lt;link rel=\"preload\"&gt;</code>; siehe <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Link_types/preload\">Preloading content with rel=\"preload\"</a> für mehr Details (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1222633\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1222633</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"css\">CSS</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Implementiert die propietären Mozilla-spezifischen Werte <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\"><code>&lt;color&gt;</code></a> <code>-moz-win-accentcolor</code> und <code>-moz-win-accentcolortext</code> (see <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1344910\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1344910</a>), und die propietäre Medienabfrage <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries#-moz-windows-accent-color-in-titlebar\">-moz-windows-accent-color-in-titlebar</a></code> (see <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1379938\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1379938</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"svg\">SVG</h3>\n\n<p><em>Keine Änderungen.</em></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl\">Intl API</a> has been enabled on Firefox for Android (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1344625\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1344625</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"apis\">APIs</h3>\n\n<h4 id=\"new_apis\">New APIs</h4>\n\n<p><em>Keine Änderungen.</em></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"dom\">DOM</h4>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Auf Macist jetzt <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/hidden\"><code>Document.hidden</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> wahr, wenn das Fenster hinter einer anderen nicht-lichtdurchlässigen Anwendung steht <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1236512\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1236512</a>.</li>\n <li>Die Eigenschaft <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/displayId\"><code>Gamepad.displayId</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> wurde implementiert (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1375816\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1375816</a>).</li>\n <li>Die Methode <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/drawImage\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.drawImage()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> wurde aktualisiert, so dass so dass die Glättung beim Downscaling erfolgt, auch wenn <code>imageSmoothingEnabled</code> ist <code>false</code>. Dies ist nicht obligatorisch wie pro Spezifikation, sondern folgt Chromes Verhalten. Siehe <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1360415\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1360415</a>.</li>\n <li>Die Eigenschaft <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/secureConnectionStart\"><code>PerformanceTiming.secureConnectionStart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> wurde implementiert (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=772589\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;772589</a>).</li>\n <li>Firefox verwendet<code> iso-2022-jp-2</code>, um Sequenzen zu nehmen, wenn ein iso-2022-jp <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder ()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> instanziiert wurde. Dies wurde nun entfernt, um die API zu vereinfachen, da keine anderen Browser oder Webseiten es unterstützen. (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=715833\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;715833</a>).</li>\n <li>Das 4ms- Klemmeverhalten von <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/setTimeout\" title=\"setTimeout()\"><code>setTimeout()</code></a> und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/setInterval\"><code>setInterval()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> wurde aktualisiert, um besser in Einklang mit anderen Browsern, wie in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/setTimeout#timeouts_throttled_to_%3e4ms\">Timeouts throttled to &gt;=4ms</a> zu sein. (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1378586\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1378586</a>).</li>\n <li>Der <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Page_Visibility_API\">Page Visibility API's</a> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/visibilitychange_event\"><code>Document.onvisibilitychange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> handler wurde hinzugefügt (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1333912\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1333912</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 id=\"dom_events\">DOM events</h4>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/wheel_event\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.onwheel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> ist ab sofort verfügbar <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> — es war nicht vorher (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1370550\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1370550</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 id=\"webrtc\">WebRTC</h4>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Firefox unterstützt nun die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Eigenschaften, die Sie die aktuellen und ausstehenden Konfigurationen der lokalen und entfernten Enden der Verbindung untersuchen lassen, um zu helfen, Änderungen in der Konfiguration zu verwalten:<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection/currentLocalDescription\"><code>currentLocalDescription</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection/pendingLocalDescription\"><code>pendingLocalDescription</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection/currentRemoteDescription\"><code>currentRemoteDescription</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection/pendingRemoteDescription\"><code>pendingRemoteDescription</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"sicherheit\">Sicherheit</h3>\n\n<p><em>Keine Änderungen.</em></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"plugins\">Plugins</h3>\n\n<p><em>Keine Änderungen.</em></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"weiteres\">Weiteres</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Gecko kodiert nun URLs intern als <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Punycode\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">punycode</a>, um URL-Codierungsprobleme zu vermeiden (siehe <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=945240\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;945240</a>, siehe auch Diskussion in <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=942074\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;942074</a>).</li>\n <li>Firefox unter Windows und Mac OS X kann nun im <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Headless_mode\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">headless Modus</a> mit der -headless-Flagge ausgeführt werden (siehe <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1355150\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1355150</a> und <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1355147\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1355147</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"von_der_web-plattform_entfernt\">Von der Web-Plattform entfernt</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"html_2\">HTML</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Das <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>&lt;isindex&gt;</code></a> Element wurde vom HTML parser und aus der Formularvorlage entfernt. (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1266495\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1266495</a>).</li>\n <li>Das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/applet\"><code>&lt;applet&gt;</code></a> Element wurde entfernt (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1279218\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1279218</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"apis_2\">APIs</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Die <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>KeyframeEffectReadOnly.spacing</code></a> Eigenschaft wurde von dem <a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'Web Animations' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations</a> spec entfernt, und deswegen wurde es auch von Gecko entfernt (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1339690\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1339690</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"svg_2\">SVG</h3>\n\n<p><em>Keine Änderungen.</em></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"änderungen_für_add-on_und_mozilla-entwickler\">Änderungen für add-on und Mozilla-Entwickler</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"webextensions\">WebExtensions</h3>\n\n<p><em>Keine Änderungen.</em></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"ältere_versionen\">Ältere Versionen</h2>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"multiColumnList\" id=\"sect2\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/55\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 55 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/54\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 54 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/53\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 53 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/52\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 52 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/51\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 51 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/50\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 50 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/49\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 49 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/48\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 48 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/47\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 47 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/46\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 46 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/45\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 45 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/44\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 44 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/43\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 43 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/42\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 42 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/41\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 41 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/40\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 40 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/39\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 39 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/38\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 38 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/37\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 37 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/36\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 36 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/35\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 35 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/34\">Firefox 34 for developers</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/33\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 33 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/32\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 32 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/31\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 31 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/30\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 30 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/29\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 29 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/28\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 28 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/27\">Firefox 27 for developers</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/26\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 26 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/25\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 25 for developers (en-US)</a></li></ul>\n</div>,<p></p>\n</article>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Änderungen für Web-Entwickler","id":"änderungen_für_web-entwickler"}],"summary":"Dieser Artikel enthält Informationen über die Änderungen in Firefox 56, die Entwickler betreffen. Firefox 56 ist die aktuelle Beta-Version von Firefox und wird am 26. September 2017 veröffentlicht werden","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Firefox 56 for developers","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Firefox 56 for developers","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"de/mozilla/firefox/releases/56","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/mozilla/firefox/releases/56/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox","title":"Firefox"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases","title":"Firefox developer release notes"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/56","title":"Firefox 56 for developers"}],"pageTitle":"Firefox 56 for developers - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}